---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Open Source - The Menon Lab">
  <article class="opensource-page">
    <h1>Open Source Projects</h1>
    
    <section class="intro">
      <p>
        Tools and libraries we've built and released to the community. 
        All MIT licensed, all actively maintained.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="projects">
      
      <!-- soul.py -->
      <div class="project-card featured">
        <div class="project-header">
          <h2>🧠 soul.py</h2>
          <span class="badge">Featured</span>
        </div>
        <p class="tagline">Persistent identity and memory for any LLM agent</p>
        <p class="description">
          Your AI forgets everything when the conversation ends. soul.py fixes that — from simple markdown injection 
          to full RAG + RLM hybrid retrieval. v0.1 uses pure markdown files. v2.0 indexes those memories and 
          automatically routes queries to semantic search (RAG) or exhaustive reasoning (RLM) based on what the question needs.
          Human-readable files you can edit and git-version, with intelligent retrieval under the hood.
        </p>
        
        <div class="version-table">
          <div class="version-row">
            <span class="version">v0.1</span>
            <span class="desc">Pure markdown, zero deps</span>
            <a href="https://soul.themenonlab.com" target="_blank" class="demo-link">Demo →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="version-row">
            <span class="version">v1.0</span>
            <span class="desc">Semantic RAG retrieval</span>
            <a href="https://soulv1.themenonlab.com" target="_blank" class="demo-link">Demo →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="version-row">
            <span class="version">v2.0</span>
            <span class="desc">Auto query routing: RAG + RLM</span>
            <a href="https://soulv2.themenonlab.com" target="_blank" class="demo-link">Demo →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/menonpg/soul.py" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">
            GitHub
          </a>
          <a href="https://pypi.org/project/soul-agent/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary">
            PyPI
          </a>
          <a href="/blog/soul-py-persistent-memory-llm-agents" class="btn btn-secondary">
            v0.1 Writeup
          </a>
          <a href="/blog/soul-py-v2-rag-rlm-hybrid" class="btn btn-secondary">
            v2.0 Writeup
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="install-block">
          <code>pip install soul-agent</code>
        </div>

        <div class="community-buzz">
          <h3>🔥 Community Response</h3>
          <p>Within hours of launch, soul.py hit <strong>#1 on r/ollama</strong> with 24K+ views.</p>
          <blockquote class="reddit-embed-bq" data-embed-height="400">
            <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/ollama/comments/1ri4d80/soulpy_persistent_memory_for_any_llm_in_10_lines/">soul.py — Persistent memory for any LLM in 10 lines (works with Ollama, no database)</a>
            <br/>by <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/the_ai_scientist/">u/the_ai_scientist</a> in <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/ollama/">r/ollama</a>
          </blockquote>
          <script async src="https://embed.reddit.com/widgets.js" charset="UTF-8"></script>
        </div>

        <div class="roadmap">
          <h3>🗺️ Roadmap</h3>
          <p>Planned features and improvements. PRs welcome!</p>
          
          <div class="roadmap-section">
            <h4>Vector Database Support</h4>
            <ul>
              <li><span class="status done">✅</span> Qdrant (current)</li>
              <li><span class="status done">✅</span> ChromaDB (local, zero-config) <em>v0.1.2</em></li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> pgvector (PostgreSQL)</li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> FAISS (local, fast)</li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> Pinecone (cloud)</li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> Weaviate</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="roadmap-section">
            <h4>Embedding Providers</h4>
            <ul>
              <li><span class="status done">✅</span> Azure OpenAI (current)</li>
              <li><span class="status done">✅</span> OpenAI direct <em>v0.1.2</em></li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> Cohere</li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> Local embeddings (sentence-transformers)</li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> Ollama embeddings</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="roadmap-section">
            <h4>CLI & Developer Experience</h4>
            <ul>
              <li><span class="status done">✅</span> <code>soul init</code> wizard</li>
              <li><span class="status done">✅</span> <code>soul chat</code> interactive CLI <em>v0.1.2</em></li>
              <li><span class="status done">✅</span> <code>soul status</code> memory stats <em>v0.1.2</em></li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> <code>config.yaml</code> file support</li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> VSCode extension</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="roadmap-section">
            <h4>Memory Features</h4>
            <ul>
              <li><span class="status done">✅</span> Timestamped conversation logging</li>
              <li><span class="status done">✅</span> RAG + RLM hybrid routing</li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> Automatic memory summarization</li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> Memory importance scoring</li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> Tiered memory (hot/warm/cold)</li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> Memory export/import</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="roadmap-section">
            <h4>Integrations</h4>
            <ul>
              <li><span class="status done">✅</span> Anthropic Claude</li>
              <li><span class="status done">✅</span> OpenAI</li>
              <li><span class="status done">✅</span> Ollama / OpenAI-compatible</li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> LangChain memory backend</li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> LlamaIndex integration</li>
              <li><span class="status planned">🔲</span> n8n node (official)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <section class="contribute">
      <h2>Want to Contribute?</h2>
      <p>
        All projects welcome PRs. Check the GitHub issues for good first contributions, 
        or open a discussion if you have ideas.
      </p>
      <a href="https://github.com/menonpg" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">
        View All Repos →
      </a>
    </section>

  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .opensource-page {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .intro {
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .intro p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .projects {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  /* Project Card */
  .project-card {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .project-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--accent);
  }

  .project-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .project-header h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }

  .badge {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .tagline {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .description {
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Version Table */
  .version-table {
    background: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.05);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .version-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .version-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .version {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: monospace;
    width: 4rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .desc {
    flex: 1;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .demo-link {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .demo-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* Project Links */
  .project-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: var(--border);
    color: var(--fg);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--muted);
    color: white;
  }

  /* Install Block */
  .install-block {
    background: #1e1e1e;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .install-block code {
    color: #4ade80;
    font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  /* Community Buzz */
  .community-buzz {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .community-buzz h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .community-buzz p {
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* Roadmap */
  .roadmap {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .roadmap > h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .roadmap > p {
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .roadmap-section {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .roadmap-section h4 {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .roadmap-section ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .roadmap-section li {
    padding: 0.25rem 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .roadmap-section code {
    background: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.1);
    padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .status {
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }

  .status.done {
    color: #4ade80;
  }

  .status.planned {
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  /* Contribute Section */
  .contribute {
    background: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.05);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contribute h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .contribute p {
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .project-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .version-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.25rem;
    }

    .project-links {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .btn {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
